{"tid":2315390,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"周梓樂死因研訊<行政會議>化.","createTime":"2020-12-07T07:09:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-07T10:33:51.000Z","uid":323449,"like":5,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"1b62f9d6e49474949a697c6b81891f67104ebfa2","tid":2315390,"uid":323449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T07:09:41.000Z","msg":"死因庭,小圈子睇片,同黑箱作業有分別嗎? 同&lt;行會&gt;有何分別?<br />\n法官指著一團黑影話-&quot;呢個就係周梓樂.&quot; 然後,小圈子死因庭全體支持法官的眼光.繼而由傳媒出來向公眾洗腦,指影片關鍵.找到周梓樂墮樓証據云云.<br />\n但其實,公眾只&quot;聽聞&quot;有&lt;一團黑影&gt;,公眾僅僅被告知影片裡&quot;並無其他人(兇手)&quot;.<br />\n相信,&quot;並無其他人(兇手)&quot;,及&quot;周梓樂黑影自已墮樓&quot;,將成為死因結論.完.<br />\n在討論區出現的截圖被裁過,會令到一些角度偏差,讓人產生錯覺.所以,這條題,會貼上全幅截圖.供人參考.對法庭扣起影片不作公開,只招侍小眾現場人士,應予譴責.<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vTbRcDG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvTbRcDG.png&h=8df0a92c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3eOL1w5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3eOL1w5.png&h=ac330d4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LkBBoLt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLkBBoLt.png&h=c8790622&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2w62jiR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2w62jiR.png&h=0f0870c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rHhQtce.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrHhQtce.png&h=5185a7a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T3eCSDW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT3eCSDW.png&h=ddd288c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ai8DB5D.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAi8DB5D.png&h=5a79ce77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0zrRcD1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0zrRcD1.png&h=1b3427c5&s={SIZE}\"